Help Type: command
Command: spinedigest

SpineDigest CLI

Purpose:
  Distill long-form EPUB, Markdown, or plain text into compressed output.
  Digesting source input uses an LLM pipeline. Re-opening an existing .sdpub archive does not.

Usage:
  spinedigest [--input <path>] [--output <path>] [--input-format <format>] [--output-format <format>] [--digest-dir <path>] [--prompt <text>] [--verbose]
  spinedigest sdpub <subcommand> --input <path> [--serial <id>]
  spinedigest help [topic]

Common paths:
  Source input -> digest -> markdown | txt | epub | .sdpub
  .sdpub input -> re-export or inspect without re-running the digest pipeline

Help topics:
{% for topic in helpTopics %}
  - spinedigest help {{ topic.name }}
    {{ topic.summary }}
{% endfor %}

sdpub subcommands:
{% for command in sdpubCommands %}
  - spinedigest sdpub {{ command.name }} --help
    {{ command.summary }}
{% endfor %}

